{"tid":1242110,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"繼樂視後，又一支那電話品牌撤出香港？","createTime":"2019-06-19T02:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T10:39:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"216ef7935c5278e50381cfa06ef749486fa93bca","tid":1242110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_20190618_214420-800x500_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FIMG_20190618_214420-800x500_c.jpg&h=ab41d81c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSUGAR 這個電話品牌曾在香港推出多款電話，相信有部份網友都認識這個主打女性的品牌。不過近期有傳，這個來自深圳的品牌將於月底就會正式撤離香港市場，並終止電話業務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Screenshot-2019-06-18-at-21.34.45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FScreenshot-2019-06-18-at-21.34.45.jpg&h=ef05ccf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據消息有傳，SUGAR 將於6月底就會結束香港業務，而於銅鑼灣中心的門市早於於5月31日已正式結業。另外，SUGAR 香港的 FACEBOOK 專頁已於近5月中開始已沒有更新，由各種跡象來看，傳聞的可信性相當高。而暫時官方還未回應這個傳聞及並沒有交代往後日子的保養問題。如果消息屬實，將會繼樂視之後，又一國產品牌敗走香港市場。<br />\n<br />\n由於近年香港智能電話市場放緩，加上品牌之間競爭激烈，讓 SUGAR 的銷量愈放愈下。近年 SUGAR 更將香港市場的對像由香港用戶轉到針對香港的外傭市場，早前更在銅鑼灣外傭集中地開設專門店，但始終仍不能扭轉劣勢。<br />\n<br />\nSUGAR-F7-MINI_02<br />\n<br />\nSUGAR 的生產商是深圳糖果通訊科技有限公司，這間公司是由天瓏移動與法國子公司於2013年成立，其後更自稱法國品牌。在早前更於機身上，裝上Swarovski Zirconia 的合成立方氧化鋯晶體作為裝飾。"},{"pid":"056f049038d34bde7dd43141ac8f234c4872128b","tid":1242110,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2019/05/samsung-galaxy-fit.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilemagazinehk.com%2F2019%2F05%2Fsamsung-galaxy-fit.html&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=5c7e2b5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mobilemagazinehk.com/2019/05/samsung-galaxy-fit.html</a>"},{"pid":"7136c73bd0c11d30b6591cee21180a65b054e56d","tid":1242110,"uid":78379,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"用MTK怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcdc4e53a02678acfcc7893742b7561f0f2ea19","tid":1242110,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:09:01.000Z","msg":"香港咁鬼細個市場<br />\n點攪啊"},{"pid":"ceeafe21f7d2eb0ce2249934db2faa48c77fcbc4","tid":1242110,"uid":61954,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:52:01.000Z","msg":"去衛訊見到攞上手玩兩玩<br />\n支米都不如<br />\n冇人買係好正常"},{"pid":"2d06566749516089a9c9d32c47b38692bc66a31b","tid":1242110,"uid":46943,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7136c73bd0c11d30b6591cee21180a65b054e56d","tid":1242110,"uid":78379,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"用MTK怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:00:27.000Z","msg":"終結者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c115a31479c0f6ffb75f91ce28f6798483da3ee","tid":1242110,"uid":22553,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"仲有 日本ask <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5383ab972cf1c1960e7a0b953e029224a1ff9c75","tid":1242110,"uid":41818,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"其後更自稱法國品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cbb4b110e71d0f7a3e5aa3dff59fe64385b177","tid":1242110,"uid":294,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"個樣仲柒過三星小米<br />\n邊個會買呀"},{"pid":"94ddd034db2e2449ecba170fc1072af1739dafe1","tid":1242110,"uid":61974,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:02:12.000Z","msg"